OAO Uralkali Gets China Approval for Silvinit Combination

-- B y   M a r i n a   S y s o y e v a
-- 
2011-06-02T17:21:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-02/oao-uralkali-gets-china-approval-for-silvinit-combination.html
OAO Uralkali,  Russia ’s largest potash
producer by market value, received  China ’s approval to merge
with OAO Silvinit.  Anti-monopoly bodies in  Brazil ,  Poland , Russia and Ukraine
already approved the deal, Uralkali said in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marina Sysoyeva in Moscow 
